<i>Lately there's been a little tension
in Phil and Lem's relationship.</i>

74
00:04:09,890 --> 00:04:12,037
Once again, your attempt
to feed the meat blob

75
00:04:12,162 --> 00:04:14,507
is being hindered
by your ridiculous use of mittens.

76
00:04:14,632 --> 00:04:18,007
- Sometimes my hands get cold.
- Because you froze yourself.

77
00:04:18,300 --> 00:04:20,176
Could we not talk about that
for one day?

78
00:04:20,344 --> 00:04:22,183
Fine. I'll feed the meat blob.

79
00:04:26,031 --> 00:04:28,641
Blobby. Like bobby,
only with an "L".

80
00:04:28,811 --> 00:04:30,768
Don't name it,
or you won't want to eat it.

81
00:04:30,938 --> 00:04:32,838
Remember Chester the carrot?

82
00:04:34,850 --> 00:04:35,900
I miss him.

83
00:04:43,897 --> 00:04:45,499
You're stealing more creamer?

84
00:04:45,624 --> 00:04:49,622
It took me 20 minutes to dry my hands,
so I am owed 20 minutes of creamer.

85
00:04:49,841 --> 00:04:52,165
- And how much is that?
- It's an infinite amount.

86
00:04:55,536 --> 00:04:57,132
I know it doesn't make sense,

87
00:04:57,257 --> 00:05:00,882
